bar_formatter <- function(values,palette = "viridis") {
  cols <- scales::col_numeric(palette, domain = NULL)(values)
  names(cols) <- values
  cols_dict = jsonlite::toJSON(as.list(cols),auto_unbox = T)

  const cols_dict = %s;

  return {fill: col}
}',cols_dict))
  formatter_code
}
